==English==

===Etymology===
Malay [[melayu]], of uncertain origin.

===Adjective===
'''Malay'''
# of or related to [[Malaysia]], its people, or its languages
# of or related to the Malays, a people living in parts of Malaysia and Indonesia

===Noun===
'''Malay'''
# the [[w:Malay language|Malay language]], an Austronesian language 
# a person of Malay ancestry

